---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import info from '../data/info.json';
---

<Layout title="Wesela i Eventy — Stara Stacja" description="Organizacja wesel i eventów na szczycie Szyndzielni. Sala na 120 osób z panoramicznym widokiem na Beskidy, profesjonalna obsługa, menu weselne.">
  <Nav />

  <!-- Hero — full-bleed photo -->
  <section class="relative h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/images/wedding/wedding-79.jpg')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/80 via-dark/40 to-dark/20"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center text-white px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <p class="text-accent-light uppercase tracking-[0.15em] sm:tracking-[0.3em] text-xs sm:text-sm mb-6 animate-fade-in">Stara Stacja Weddings</p>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-bold mb-6">
        <span class="text-pl">Wyjątkowe chwile</span>
        <span class="text-en hidden">Exceptional Moments</span>
        <span class="text-cs hidden">Výjimečné chvíle</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-light text-white/80 mb-10">
        <span class="text-pl">1000 metrów nad poziomem morza</span>
        <span class="text-en hidden">1,000 meters above sea level</span>
        <span class="text-cs hidden">1 000 metrů nad mořem</span>
      </p>
      <a href="#kontakt" class="inline-block px-10 py-4 bg-accent text-primary font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm hover:bg-accent-light transition-colors">
        <span class="text-pl">Zaplanuj wesele</span>
        <span class="text-en hidden">Plan your wedding</span>
        <span class="text-cs hidden">Naplánujte svatbu</span>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
      <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white/60" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
      </svg>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro — text + couple photo -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-sm mb-3">
          <span class="text-pl">Wesele w chmurach</span>
          <span class="text-en hidden">Wedding in the clouds</span>
          <span class="text-cs hidden">Svatba v oblacích</span>
        </p>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
          <span class="text-pl">Idealne miejsce na przyjęcie weselne</span>
          <span class="text-en hidden">The perfect wedding reception venue</span>
          <span class="text-cs hidden">Ideální místo pro svatební hostinu</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          <span class="text-pl">Stara Stacja to wyjątkowa restauracja, położona na szczycie malowniczej Szyndzielni, z panoramicznym widokiem na Beskidy i miasto Bielsko-Białą. Profesjonalna obsługa, wspaniała kuchnia i świetnie zaprojektowana przestrzeń sprawiają, że jest to idealne miejsce na przyjęcie weselne.</span>
          <span class="text-en hidden">Stara Stacja is a unique restaurant located at the summit of picturesque Szyndzielnia, with a panoramic view of the Beskid Mountains and Bielsko-Biała. Professional service, wonderful cuisine, and beautifully designed space make it the perfect venue for a wedding reception.</span>
          <span class="text-cs hidden">Stara Stacja je výjimečná restaurace na vrcholu malebné Szyndzielnie s panoramatickým výhledem na Beskydy a město Bielsko-Bílá. Profesionální obsluha, skvělá kuchyně a krásně navržený prostor z ní činí ideální místo pro svatební hostinu.</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
          <span class="text-pl">Organizujemy również konferencje, szkolenia, spotkania firmowe i inne wydarzenia specjalne. Możemy dostosować każdy aspekt imprezy do Waszych potrzeb.</span>
          <span class="text-en hidden">We also organize conferences, training sessions, corporate meetings, and other special events. We can customize every aspect of your event to your needs.</span>
          <span class="text-cs hidden">Pořádáme také konference, školení, firemní setkání a další speciální akce. Každý aspekt události můžeme přizpůsobit vašim potřebám.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-sm overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/wedding/wedding-69.jpg" alt="Para młoda w sali Starej Stacji" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 left-0 sm:-left-6 bg-accent text-primary px-4 sm:px-6 py-3 sm:py-4 font-heading text-base sm:text-lg font-bold">
          <span class="text-pl">do 120 gości</span>
          <span class="text-en hidden">up to 120 guests</span>
          <span class="text-cs hidden">až 120 hostů</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Photo strip — 3 images edge-to-edge -->
  <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-1">
    <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden">
      <img src="/images/wedding/wedding-31.jpg" alt="Dekoracja stołu weselnego" class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden">
      <img src="/images/wedding/wedding-95.jpg" alt="Para młoda przy zabytkowym wagoniku" class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden">
      <img src="/images/wedding/wedding-32.jpg" alt="Dekoracja florystyczna" class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Space features — with photos -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-primary text-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-sm mb-3">
          <span class="text-pl">Nasza przestrzeń</span>
          <span class="text-en hidden">Our space</span>
          <span class="text-cs hidden">Náš prostor</span>
        </p>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold">
          <span class="text-pl">Co oferujemy</span>
          <span class="text-en hidden">What we offer</span>
          <span class="text-cs hidden">Co nabízíme</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 1: Hall — photo left, text right -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
        <div class="aspect-[3/2] rounded-sm overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/wedding/wedding-135.jpg" alt="Panorama sali weselnej" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
            <span class="text-pl">Przestronna sala 300m²</span>
            <span class="text-en hidden">Spacious 300m² hall</span>
            <span class="text-cs hidden">Prostorný sál 300m²</span>
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span>
              <span>
                <span class="text-pl">Panoramiczny widok na góry i Bielsko-Białą, do 120 osób</span>
                <span class="text-en hidden">Panoramic mountain and city views, up to 120 guests</span>
                <span class="text-cs hidden">Panoramatický výhled na hory a Bielsko-Bílou, až 120 hostů</span>
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span>
              <span>
                <span class="text-pl">Autentyczny klimat dawnej stacji kolejki linowej</span>
                <span class="text-en hidden">Authentic atmosphere of a former cable car station</span>
                <span class="text-cs hidden">Autentická atmosféra bývalé stanice lanovky</span>
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span>
              <span>
                <span class="text-pl">Klimatyczny kominek idealny na jesienno-zimowe przyjęcia</span>
                <span class="text-en hidden">Atmospheric fireplace perfect for autumn and winter receptions</span>
                <span class="text-cs hidden">Atmosférický krb ideální pro podzimní a zimní oslavy</span>
              </span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2: Gondola — text left, photo right -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
        <div class="md:order-2 aspect-[3/2] rounded-sm overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/wedding/wedding-114.jpg" alt="Para młoda przy gondoli kolejki linowej" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="md:order-1">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
            <span class="text-pl">Wyjątkowy charakter</span>
            <span class="text-en hidden">Unique character</span>
            <span class="text-cs hidden">Jedinečný charakter</span>
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span>
              <span>
                <span class="text-pl">Ekspozycja historycznych wagoników kolejki linowej z lat 1953–2016</span>
                <span class="text-en hidden">Exhibition of historic cable car gondolas from 1953–2016</span>
                <span class="text-cs hidden">Expozice historických kabinek lanovky z let 1953–2016</span>
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span>
              <span>
                <span class="text-pl">Taras jako strefa chillout z plenerowym barem — możliwość wynajmu na wyłączność</span>
                <span class="text-en hidden">Terrace as a chill-out zone with outdoor bar — available for exclusive rental</span>
                <span class="text-cs hidden">Terasa jako chill-out zóna s venkovním barem — k pronájmu na výhradní použití</span>
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent mt-1 shrink-0">&bull;</span>
              <span>
                <span class="text-pl">Dodatkowa przestrzeń na ceremonię w plenerze</span>
                <span class="text-en hidden">Additional space for an outdoor ceremony</span>
                <span class="text-cs hidden">Další prostor pro obřad venku</span>
              </span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3: Highlights row -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
        <div class="bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-sm">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8.25 18.75a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m3 0h6m-9 0H3.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V14.25m17.25 4.5a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m3 0H21M3.375 14.25h17.25M3.375 14.25A1.125 1.125 0 012.25 13.125V6.375A1.125 1.125 0 013.375 5.25h17.25A1.125 1.125 0 0121.75 6.375v6.75A1.125 1.125 0 0120.625 14.25" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold mb-2">
            <span class="text-pl">Kolejka linowa w cenie</span>
            <span class="text-en hidden">Cable car included</span>
            <span class="text-cs hidden">Lanovka v ceně</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">
            <span class="text-pl">Przejazd w dwie strony dla wszystkich gości</span>
            <span class="text-en hidden">Round-trip for all guests</span>
            <span class="text-cs hidden">Zpáteční jízda pro všechny hosty</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-sm">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold mb-2">
            <span class="text-pl">Ceremonia w plenerze</span>
            <span class="text-en hidden">Outdoor ceremony</span>
            <span class="text-cs hidden">Obřad venku</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">
            <span class="text-pl">Przestrzeń na ślub pod gołym niebem</span>
            <span class="text-en hidden">Space for an open-air wedding</span>
            <span class="text-cs hidden">Prostor pro svatbu pod širým nebem</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-sm">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 6.042A8.967 8.967 0 006 3.75c-1.052 0-2.062.18-3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 016 18c2.305 0 4.408.867 6 2.292m0-14.25a8.966 8.966 0 016-2.292c1.052 0 2.062.18 3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0018 18a8.967 8.967 0 00-6 2.292m0-14.25v14.25" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold mb-2">
            <span class="text-pl">Menu na każdą dietę</span>
            <span class="text-en hidden">Menus for every diet</span>
            <span class="text-cs hidden">Menu pro každou dietu</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">
            <span class="text-pl">Dostosowanie do różnych wymagań</span>
            <span class="text-en hidden">Adapted to different requirements</span>
            <span class="text-cs hidden">Přizpůsobení různým požadavkům</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Menu packages -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-sm mb-3">
          <span class="text-pl">Przykładowe menu</span>
          <span class="text-en hidden">Sample menus</span>
          <span class="text-cs hidden">Ukázková menu</span>
        </p>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">
          <span class="text-pl">Pakiety weselne</span>
          <span class="text-en hidden">Wedding packages</span>
          <span class="text-cs hidden">Svatební balíčky</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-dark/50 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <span class="text-pl">Możliwość dostosowania menu do różnego typu diet</span>
          <span class="text-en hidden">Menus can be adapted to different dietary requirements</span>
          <span class="text-cs hidden">Menu lze přizpůsobit různým typům diet</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
        <!-- Package 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/images/wedding/wedding-62.jpg" alt="Stół weselny" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 lg:p-10">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-1">
              <span class="text-pl">"Ruszamy w Góry"</span>
              <span class="text-en hidden">"Heading to the Mountains"</span>
              <span class="text-cs hidden">"Vyrážíme do hor"</span>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-accent font-heading text-3xl font-bold mb-8">349 zł <span class="text-base font-normal text-dark/40">
              <span class="text-pl">/ os.</span>
              <span class="text-en hidden">/ person</span>
              <span class="text-cs hidden">/ os.</span>
            </span></p>

            <div class="space-y-5 text-sm">
              <div>
                <h4 class="uppercase tracking-wider text-accent text-xs font-semibold mb-1">
                  <span class="text-pl">Toast powitalny</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Welcome toast</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Uvítací přípitek</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-dark/70">
                  <span class="text-pl">Lampka prosecco</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Glass of prosecco</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Sklenka prosecca</span>
                </p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h4 class="uppercase tracking-wider text-accent text-xs font-semibold mb-1">
                  <span class="text-pl">Uroczysty obiad</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Formal dinner</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Slavnostní oběd</span>
                </h4>
                <ul class="text-dark/70 space-y-1">
                  <li>
                    <span class="text-pl">Austriacki bulion</span>
                    <span class="text-en hidden">Austrian bouillon</span>
                    <span class="text-cs hidden">Rakouský bujón</span>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <span class="text-pl">Rolada z kurczaka z serem w sosie ziołowym z pieczonymi ziemniakami i surówką</span>
                    <span class="text-en hidden">Chicken roulade with cheese in herb sauce, roasted potatoes and salad</span>
                    <span class="text-cs hidden">Kuřecí roláda se sýrem v bylinkové omáčce s pečenými bramborami a salátem</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h4 class="uppercase tracking-wider text-accent text-xs font-semibold mb-1">
                  <span class="text-pl">Kolacja</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Supper</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Večeře</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-dark/70">
                  <span class="text-pl">Barszcz z krokietem</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Beetroot soup with croquette</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Boršč s kroketou</span>
                </p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h4 class="uppercase tracking-wider text-accent text-xs font-semibold mb-1">
                  <span class="text-pl">Bufety</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Buffets</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Bufety</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-dark/70">
                  <span class="text-pl">Słodki bufet (3 porcje/os.) + bufet słonych przekąsek</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Sweet buffet (3 portions/person) + savory snacks buffet</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Sladký bufet (3 porce/os.) + bufet slaných občerstvení</span>
                </p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h4 class="uppercase tracking-wider text-accent text-xs font-semibold mb-1">
                  <span class="text-pl">Napoje</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Beverages</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Nápoje</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-dark/70">
                  <span class="text-pl">Woda gaz/niegaz, 2 rodzaje soków, kawa i herbata</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Sparkling/still water, 2 types of juice, coffee and tea</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Perlivá/neperlivá voda, 2 druhy džusů, káva a čaj</span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Package 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/images/wedding/wedding-41.jpg" alt="Eleganckie nakrycie stołu" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 lg:p-10">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-1">
              <span class="text-pl">"Droga na Szczyt"</span>
              <span class="text-en hidden">"Road to the Summit"</span>
              <span class="text-cs hidden">"Cesta na vrchol"</span>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-accent font-heading text-3xl font-bold mb-8">429 zł <span class="text-base font-normal text-dark/40">
              <span class="text-pl">/ os.</span>
              <span class="text-en hidden">/ person</span>
              <span class="text-cs hidden">/ os.</span>
            </span></p>

            <div class="space-y-5 text-sm">
              <div>
                <h4 class="uppercase tracking-wider text-accent text-xs font-semibold mb-1">
                  <span class="text-pl">Toast powitalny</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Welcome toast</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Uvítací přípitek</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-dark/70">
                  <span class="text-pl">Lampka prosecco</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Glass of prosecco</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Sklenka prosecca</span>
                </p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h4 class="uppercase tracking-wider text-accent text-xs font-semibold mb-1">
                  <span class="text-pl">Przystawka</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Appetizer</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Předkrm</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-dark/70">
                  <span class="text-pl">Gravlax z łososia</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Salmon gravlax</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Gravlax z lososa</span>
                </p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h4 class="uppercase tracking-wider text-accent text-xs font-semibold mb-1">
                  <span class="text-pl">Uroczysty obiad</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Formal dinner</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Slavnostní oběd</span>
